outputs
: Custom tests can return elements like tables or plots. Tables may be a list of dictionaries (each representing a row) or a [pandas DataFrame](https://pandas.pydata.org/docs/reference/api/pandas.DataFrame.html). Plots may be [matplotlib](https://matplotlib.org/) or [plotly](https://plotly.com/) figures.
